# Photo Gallery

Browse all photos in the workspace. Click any image to view in lightbox mode.

## Features

- **Grid layout** with 4 columns
- **Lightbox** for full-size viewing
- **Metadata** display with EXIF data
- **Keyboard navigation** (arrow keys in lightbox)
